  _push(`</a></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013112000619" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013112000619.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>当你下载完成之后，你会得到如下文件</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013112130043" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013112130043.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><h3 id="安装过程化" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#安装过程化" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 安装过程化</h3><ol><li><p>双击点击安装</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013112222351" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013112222351.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p></li><li><p>选择一个安装目录</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013132648644" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013132648644.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>这里的安装目录可以随便选择，<code>但是一定要记得此路径，在后面需要使用到</code></p></li><li><p>点击next</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128222436169" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128222436169.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><div class="custom-container warning"><p class="custom-container-title">WARNING</p><p>这里一定要选择<code>Add to PATH</code>，一定要记得选择<code>Add to PATH</code>，一定要记得选择<code>Add to PATH</code></p></div><p>这里还是点击next</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013132911956" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013132911956.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013132930873" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013132930873.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013133002992" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013133002992.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p></li></ol><p>​ 然后等待安装完成之后，就可以了</p><h3 id="设置环境和变量" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#设置环境和变量" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 设置环境和变量</h3><div class="custom-container tip"><p class="custom-container-title">TIP</p><p>因为之前选择了<code>App to PATH</code>，所以我们值需要简单设置一下就行</p></div><h4 id="验证" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#验证" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 验证</h4><p>上一步安装完成之后，按住<code>win r</code>键，输入<code>cmd</code></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013133147151" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013133147151.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>在面板中，输入<code>node -v</code>验证是否安装成功</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013133235630" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013133235630.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>当出现<code>v14.17.3</code>时，表示node已经安装成功了，此值也有可能不同，取决于你下的node版本</p><h4 id="设置" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#设置" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 设置</h4><ol><li><p>进入上一步安装node的目录中，你将看到如下文件</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013133600368" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013133600368.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p></li><li><p>在此目录中，新建<code>node_cache</code>和<code>node_global</code>两个文件夹</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013133711581" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013133711581.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p></li><li><p>在<code>cmd</code>面板中，运行下面两个命令，一个一个的运行</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token builtin class-name">set</span> prefix <span class="token string">&quot;D:\\Develop<span class="token entity" title="\\n">\\n</span>odejs<span class="token entity" title="\\n">\\n</span>ode_global&quot;</span>
<span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token builtin class-name">set</span> cache <span class="token string">&quot;D:\\Develop<span class="token entity" title="\\n">\\n</span>odejs<span class="token entity" title="\\n">\\n</span>ode_cache&quot;</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div><div class="custom-container tip"><p class="custom-container-title">TIP</p><p>将后面的路径改成你自己对应文件夹就行</p></div></li><li><p>然后再运行下面这个命令</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">npm</span> config <span class="token builtin class-name">set</span> <span class="token assign-left variable">registry</span><span class="token operator">=</span>http://registry.npm.taobao.org/ 
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>使用淘宝镜像，不然下载速度非常慢</p></li><li><p>设置环境变量</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013134927339" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013134927339.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013134955551" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013134955551.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211013135021613" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211013135021613.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p></li></ol><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128225456194" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128225456194.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128225939601" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128225939601.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>设置好之后，点击确定就行了</p><h3 id="验证-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#验证-1" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 验证</h3><p>现在验证一下，刚才安装的是否正确</p><p>打开cmd面板，运行下面命令</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">npm</span> root-g
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128230349713" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128230349713.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>如果输入命令之后，输出的<code>node_modules</code>前面的路径就是你刚才创建的<code>node_global</code>的路径，那么就表示你设置成功</p><h3 id="验证脚手架" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#验证脚手架" aria-hidden="true">#</a> 验证脚手架</h3><div class="custom-container tip"><p class="custom-container-title">TIP</p><p>一定要先验证<code>aurora</code>命令是否可用，否则安装主题会有点麻烦</p></div><p>在<code>cmd</code>中输入下面命令安装Aurora脚手架</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token function">npm</span> i vuepress-theme-cli -g
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br></div></div><p>待下载成功之后，在控制台中输入<code>aurora blog</code>，然后按回车</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128231157929" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128231157929.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>如果提示下图</p><div class="custom-container warning"><p class="custom-container-title">WARNING</p><div class="language-bash ext-sh line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-bash"><code><span class="token string">&#39;aurora&#39;</span> 不是内部或外部命令，也不是可运行的程序
或批处理文件。
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br></div></div></div><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128231224969" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128231224969.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><p>进入到环境变量中，新建一个，输入<a href="#%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE">创建的node_global路径</a></p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128231434520" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128231434520.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p><div class="custom-container tip"><p class="custom-container-title">TIP</p><p>正常情况，你输入<code>aurora blog</code>之后，便会下载一个模板</p><p><img src="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-public/ljz.gif" alt="image-20211128231837831" originSrc="https://ooszy.cco.vin/img/blog-note/image-20211128231837831.png?x-oss-process=style/pictureProcess1" data="aurora"></p></div><p>然后现在你可以了</p><p>根据面板中的指示，运行相应命令，就可以启动博客了</p><!--]-->`)
